high_descs: Go straight and then take a right into the kitchen to the countertop.
Pick up the bread in front of the microwave.
Turn around and go to the fridge behind you.
Put the bread in the refrigerator and then take the bread back out.
Turn around and go back into the living room to the brown sidetable under the window on your right.
Put the bread on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put a loaf of chilled bread on the SideTable in the living room.

high_descs: Keep moving forward. Cross to the right. Go to the countertop.
Take the bread from the kitchen counter.
Turn around, move until you are parallel to the fridge. Turn right.
Open the top doors of the refrigerator. Put the bread on the second level. Close the door. Wait eleven seconds and open the door. Take out the bread. Close the door.
Turn left, go straight ahead to the sidetable. Turn right.
Place the bread on the right side of the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Find a loaf of Bread, cool it and place it on a SideTable.

high_descs: Stand up turn around move towards the countertop.
Take the bread from the countertop.
Turn around move towards the fridge.
Keep the bread inside the fridge and take it back.
Turn around move towards the side table.
Keep the bread on the side table.
anns.task_desc: Take the bread, keep it inside the fridge and keep it on the side table.
